<HEADLINE>
FT  10 MAY 93 / People: Public posts
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
John Swain, md of Anopol, has been elected chairman of the METAL FINISHING
ASSOCIATION.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
