<HEADLINE>
FT  10 MAY 93 / Construction Contracts: Colchester housing scheme
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MANSELL has been awarded Phases 3 and 4 of a residential design and build
scheme for clients The Guinness Trust. Providing a 123-unit development in
Highwoods, Colchester, the scheme has a value of Pounds 4m with completion
anticipated mid-1994.
The design of the scheme has been prepared in collaboration with the John
Groom Association, providing groups of bungalows for the disabled. The
bungalows comply to the John Groom building specification incorporating
extra wide doors for ease of wheelchair access; ramps and dropped kerbs
around the entire development; specially equipped toilets, bathrooms and
kitchens.
</TEXT>
